        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8087",
        "content": "The boy was at once taken on board and rated as a seaman; and the later adventures of the trip are here given as he reported them on his return with the ship some months later.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
