        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8087",
        "content": "As night came on they made a fire at the base of a fallen oak, near the shore, and lay around it, talking, and smoking the lately discovered weed, tobacco; when suddenly they heard loud noises from the direction of the castle and then all over the island, which frightened them so that they went on board the sloop and stayed all night.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
