        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8087",
        "content": "Hailing the sloop, the older gentleman, speaking Gaelic, asked who and whence they were, and being told, invited them ashore as his guests.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
